UserOptionDefinition.Device_DanceVolume_C.Tempo.Description: Controls the rate at which rhythmic emotes play.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_DanceVolume_C.DeactivateEmoteLead: Deactivate the emote leader behavior on receiving a signal from the selected channel.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_DanceVolume_C.InvertClassSelectio: Determines if all classes except the selected class are affected by this volume.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_DanceVolume_C.InvertTeamSelection: Determines if all teams except the selected team are affected by this volume.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_DanceVolume_C.DefaultEmote.Descri: Determines the active emote that the volume will use by default.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_DanceVolume_C.EnabledOnPhase.Desc: Determines the game phases during which the device will be enabled. Pre-Game includes all phases prior to the Game starting (the waiting for players lobby on Featured Islands and the Game Start Countdown).
UserOptionDefinition.Device_DanceVolume_C.SelectedClass.Descr: Determines what class is affected by this volume.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_DanceVolume_C.SelectedTeam.Descri: Determines what team is affected by this volume.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_DanceVolume_C.MuteEmoteAudio.Desc: Determines whether emotes triggered by the volume will play their own audio.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_DanceVolume_C.RhythmicallySyncEmo: Determines whether rhythmic emotes will sync to a tempo.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_DanceVolume_C.AutomaticallyPlayEm: Determines whether the volume’s active emote will automatically play.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_DanceVolume_C.ZoneVisibleDuringGa: Determines whether the zone is visible during the game.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_DanceVolume_C.Disable.Description: Disables the device on receiving a signal from the selected channel.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_DanceVolume_C.Enable.Description: Enables the device on receiving a signal from the selected channel.
